OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FPatchy rain
OL,6,Fat first, becoming more persistent,
OL,7,Fand locally heavy, through the
OL,8,Fevening. This clearing eastern coasts
OL,9,Fbefore dawn, with dry conditions and
OL,10,Foccasional spells following. Generally
OL,11,Fmilder than previous nights.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSunday:FGenerally a dry and bright
OL,14,Fstart, far eastern coasts cloudier
OL,15,Finitially. Isolated showers in the far
OL,16,Fwest from midday, spreading east into
OL,17,Fthe evening and becoming heavy in
OL,18,Fplaces.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
