OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FMonday
OL,6,Fsunshine and scattered heavy showers.
OL,7,FRain and strong winds overnight,
OL,8,Fclears Tuesday with windy conditions
OL,9,Fand showers following. Wednesday
OL,10,Fbreezy, bright spells and isolated
OL,11,Fshowers. Temperatures becoming warmer.
